PROCESS      HELP=*

PARM INP       TYPE=STRING COUNT=0:9
PARM MULTIMETA TYPE=STRING COUNT=0:1 DEFAULT=""
PARM PANMETA   TYPE=STRING COUNT=0:1 DEFAULT=""
PARM BAND      TYPE=INTEGER COUNT=0:1 DEFAULT=0 VALID=(0:9)
PARM OUT       TYPE=STRING COUNT=0:9

END-PROC

.TITLE
VICAR/IBIS Program "wv2ref"
.HELP
PURPOSE
 This program converts raw dn images
 into top of atmosphere reflectance 
 images where the values range from 
 0 to 1.  The output image(s) is in 
 "REAL" format. 

.LEVEL1
.VARIABLE INP
 Input raw dn worldview2 image(s).
 The number of inputs must
 be either 1 or all 9 bands.
 !!! PAN BAND IS 9 !!!

.VARIABLE OUT
 Output reflectance image(s).
 Either 1 or all 9 bands depending
 on the input
 !!! PAN BAND IS 9 !!!

.VARIABLE MULTIMETA
 .IMD file containing metadata
 regarding the multispectral
 input images.

.VARIABLE PANMETA
 .IMD file containing metadata
 regarding the pan input image

.VARIABLE BAND
 Specifies which band the input
 image is.  Ignored if all 9
 bands are input.
 !!! PAN BAND IS 9 !!!
 Coastal=1
 Blue=2
 Green=3
 Yellow=4
 Red=5
 Red Edge=6
 NIR1=7
 NIR2=8
 Pan=9

.END











